# C4 Level 1 — System Context
# Taible and the people and external systems around it.

direction: right

customer: Diner {
  shape: person
}
partner: Restaurant Partner {
  shape: person
}

taible: Taible Platform {
  style.fill: "#e8f0fe"
}

payment_network: Crypto Payment Network {
  shape: cloud
}
pos: Restaurant POS / Delivery Systems {
  shape: cloud
}

customer -> taible: Browses, orders, pays (mobile app)
partner -> taible: Onboards, manages menu and orders
taible -> payment_network: Settles payments
taible <-> pos: Syncs menu and orders
